These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, chinchilla, dog
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person eating mango is the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Pet   | turtle  | hedgehog     | chinchilla   | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, red, orange, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the person who likes black is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | orange | black | red | light-blue    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Pet   | cat   | guinea-pig | rabbit | ferret         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game, prince, fonseca
1. the game-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| Cigar         | game | fonseca   | prince | bolivar |

