.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, july, may
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Birthday    | november       | may | july | december     |

