2. the engineer is on the far right##1
3. the software-developer is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the project-manager is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Job   | software-developer | project-manager | mechanic | engineer  |
| Pet           | mouse | chinchilla | rat       | ferret |

