.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, canadian, indonesian, italian
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the person driving the trike is the italian##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality         | indonesian | pakistani      | canadian | italian |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

