.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, gospel, hip-hop
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | gospel | pop          | classical    |

