.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, emerald, pink, yellow
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Color   | aquamarine  | pink | yellow           | emerald   |

