3. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
