3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the cottage house##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | horror | western | comedy |
| House     | gothic-revival | ranch-style    | cottage  | townhouse |

