.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, rock-climbing, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, brown, aquamarine, light-blue
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | rock-climbing | video-games | cooking |
| Color   | light-blue     | aquamarine    | blue      | brown   |

