.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, may, september
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | june | may | november | september   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 